# whisper

> Convert audio files to txt,vtt,srt,tsv,json
> Help: --help
> More information: https://github.com/openai/whisper

- Convert a specific audio file to all file formats:

`whisper {/?file mp3 audio}`

- Convert an audio file to a specific file format:

`whisper {/?file mp3 audio} --output-format {string format: txt}`

- Convert an audio file to all file formats with a specific conversion model:

`whisper {/?file mp3 audio} --model {string model: tiny.en, tiny, base.en, base, small.en, small, medium.en, medium, large-v1, large-v2, large}`

- Convert an audio file to all file formats with a specific language:

`whisper {/?file mp3 audio} --language {string language: english}`

- Convert an audio file to all file formats to a specific directory:

`whisper {/?file mp3 audio} --output_dir "{string some description: path/to/output}"`

- Convert a specific audio file to all file formats being in verbose mode:

`whisper {/?file mp3 audio} --verbose {bool whether to enable verbose mode: True, False}`